Setup instructions:
Change project name in .bat file
Create link, move to desktop
Right click link, properties
To run with a minimized command window:
Run -> minimized

* there is a way to have the cmd prompt not show at all, 
it removes the ability for killing the process if it hangs by X-ing out of the command prompt
currently MTPcontrol 'hangs' if the probe isn't actually on, so this is still necessary. 
